2026-05-15T18:39:48.9161087Z 12    <!--
2026-05-15T18:39:48.9161458Z 13        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-15T18:39:48.9191994Z 14        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-15T18:39:48.9192620Z 15        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-15T18:39:48.9192908Z 16        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-15T18:39:48.9193309Z 17        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
