2026-05-15T18:39:48.9697766Z 249            Harden Google Play Billing's proxy activities so the system
2026-05-15T18:39:48.9698129Z 250            cannot restore them from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-15T18:39:48.9698502Z 251            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-15T18:39:48.9698863Z 252            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-15T18:39:48.9699111Z 253            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-15T18:39:48.9699521Z 254            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-15T18:39:48.9699900Z 255            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-15T18:39:48.9700517Z 256            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-15T18:39:48.9700895Z 257            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
